title: Gobble Cross
description: GobbleCross is a local cyclocross race, organized and directed by the Oklahoma State University Cycling Club and scored in correspondence with OKCXGP.
course: The GobbleCross course utilizes the Couch Park facilities and features a multitude of grass, dirt trails, off camber corners and several trademark cyclocross attributes.
